        "locales": {
            "en": {
                "name": "6B47 Ratnik-BSh upgraded helmet (Black)",
                "shortName": "6B47-U Black",
                "description": "An upgraded 6B47 Ratnik-BSh helmet finished in matte black. Originally developed as a lightweight aramid helmet for the Ratnik program, this modified version has been reinforced with additional ballistic material and improved internal padding. The upgrade increases protection to Class 5 while retaining the standard mounts for lights and night vision devices. Heavier than the original, but built for people who expect the shooting to start before negotiations do."
